Class IXMultiObjectConflictResolver

    public class IXMultiObjectConflictResolver
extends IXDefaultConflictResolver
    A marker class to indicate that the resolver is capable of resolving conflict which may be related to many objects in an import session. It provides the default resolution, it leaves it to the importer to resolve the conflict in any manner it likes, if it can.
    • Default resolution:
      • Default resolution as per importer.
    • Available resolution:
      • Default resolution as per importer.
      • Skip object import.


    Supported API: true
